Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.93,0:01:50.10,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah～是否可以遇見有如魔法的那瞬間？\N{\c&HFFBF00&}Ah～魔法のような一瞬に会えるのか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.17,0:02:04.52,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,取代寒冷的黑夜  我倆展翅飛翔\N{\c&HFFBF00&}冷たい夜を引き替えに  二人は羽ばたいて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.59,0:02:13.26,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在那盡頭  抓住了永恆…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}永远を掴む、その果てには
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.07,0:02:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}戴芬妮女王\NQueen Delphine
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.73,0:02:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副艦長，艦長他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.23,0:02:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.76,0:02:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且迪奧和艾兒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.20,0:02:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有克勞士他們\N都被那位總帥給帶走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.24,0:02:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士也被帶走了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.07,0:03:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要帶走克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.72,0:03:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.16,0:03:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.03,0:03:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.70,0:03:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得呢，魯修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.57,0:03:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜您了，戴芬妮陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.30,0:03:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.77,0:03:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.81,0:03:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧他怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.25,0:03:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道迪奧他\N為什麼那麼怕妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.88,0:03:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳打算抹殺迪奧他的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.95,0:03:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.35,0:03:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們感情可好的很呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.56,0:03:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉你都不在乎嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.97,0:04:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.94,0:04:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這世界是屬於我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.27,0:04:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們也來幫他慶祝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.84,0:04:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧今天就要變大人了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.26,0:04:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總帥萬歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.53,0:04:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總帥萬歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.27,0:04:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫做克勞士是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.34,0:04:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很想知道\N這片天空發生了什麼事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.28,0:04:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我的話，就可以告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.12,0:04:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天空是屬於我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.49,0:04:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道我在做些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.35,0:04:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就等於知道了\N你所想知道的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.19,0:04:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宣誓儀式開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.29,0:05:01.92,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,我心與天空同在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.00,0:05:04.33,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,與白雲共存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.40,0:05:06.42,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,藍天解放了我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.50,0:05:09.40,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,尊榮的銅牆鐵壁\N守護我們免於地上煉火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.47,0:05:12.17,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,我們願獻身給天上的風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.24,0:05:14.71,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,直到攸久之時光盡頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.78,0:05:16.90,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,在藍天白雲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.98,0:05:18.88,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,與紅牆的環繞裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.95,0:05:20.61,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,我們將守衛祖國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.68,0:05:22.88,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,我們與天空同在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.39,0:05:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.65,0:05:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臉上刻有宣誓印記的\N未來領袖們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.59,0:05:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一個世代的基爾特\N將由你們來打造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.46,0:05:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基爾特是法律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.33,0:05:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基爾特是秩序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.37,0:05:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基爾特就是世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.77,0:05:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追求的是永恆的安寧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.91,0:05:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請賜予世界永恆的安寧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.21,0:05:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚給忠誠的獎勵將很特別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.81,0:05:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一代的基爾特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.92,0:06:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宣誓之劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.76,0:06:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有為基爾特帶來永恆的人\N才能夠擁有這把劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.66,0:06:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若想繼承我的名號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.66,0:06:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就拿起這把宣誓之劍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.97,0:06:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後勝利的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.17,0:06:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我將賜予這總帥的頭銜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.80,0:06:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劍只有一把
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.67,0:06:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你們以靈魂來宣誓的人數呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.15,0:06:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們明白了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.91,0:06:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是今晚成人儀式的考驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.92,0:06:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，這就開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.06,0:06:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.06,0:06:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳打算叫他做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.93,0:06:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是迪奧他姊姊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.33,0:06:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快阻止他啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.37,0:06:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我偏不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.42,0:07:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了，迪奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.35,0:07:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是在天空所發生的事\N克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.69,0:07:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基爾特宣誓儀式的時間到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.73,0:07:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全軍準備進攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.90,0:07:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備進攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.24,0:07:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.27,0:07:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，這是朋友給我的生還章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.81,0:07:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是手製的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.94,0:07:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.04,0:07:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.74,0:07:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果集滿了20枚生還章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.88,0:07:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以昇級\N並選擇自己喜歡的船艦搭乘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.98,0:07:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.98,0:07:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.39,0:07:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.79,0:07:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在拿到這次作戰的\N第20枚生還章之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.02,0:07:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就好比是我的護身符一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.97,0:07:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是他朋友的話\N就好好看清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.77,0:08:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看迪奧他有多美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.05,0:08:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒，怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.82,0:08:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴芬妮陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.35,0:08:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是巨繭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.92,0:08:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒‧薇絲，接下來的主角是妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.09,0:08:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快過來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.06,0:08:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，迪奧呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.53,0:08:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要知道結果就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.43,0:08:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是萬一他死了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.80,0:08:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是他自己不對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.54,0:08:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只想知道\N是誰會繼承我的名號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.21,0:08:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，快帶艾兒‧薇絲過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.41,0:08:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.48,0:08:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我戴芬妮叫你帶她過來\N你就給我帶過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.90,0:09:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.77,0:09:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是苦了妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.44,0:09:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帥哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.64,0:09:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.45,0:09:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.68,0:09:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙偏偏就這種時候不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.59,0:09:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去接克勞士回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.82,0:09:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,順便到基爾特逛逛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.39,0:09:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳都沒聽說嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.86,0:09:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在起要殺進基爾特呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.53,0:09:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦被砍就要砍回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.43,0:09:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是殺無赦銀之戰艦的規矩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.40,0:09:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還要砍它個三倍才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.14,0:09:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可怕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.51,0:09:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊薩，還不快把裝備拿來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.31,0:09:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，我這就去拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.65,0:09:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇把先鋒艇修好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.72,0:09:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.22,0:09:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.69,0:09:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.29,0:09:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這在哪裡找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.19,0:10:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看它被丟在休息室裡\N就把它拿來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.20,0:10:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這畫的是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.87,0:10:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒說是她夢到的風景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.27,0:10:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.57,0:10:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要去把\N克勞士和艾兒救回來才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.17,0:10:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都畫到這個地步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.48,0:10:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總該讓人家好好畫完吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.41,0:10:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然都已經修好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.81,0:10:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆就駕著克勞士的先鋒艇\N給它殺過去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.78,0:10:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要說蠢話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.45,0:10:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊長…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.89,0:10:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士和拉薇的先鋒艇\N並不是戰鬥機好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.90,0:10:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.43,0:10:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.33,0:10:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.71,0:10:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望不會發生流血事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.87,0:10:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把槍藏起來，快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.64,0:10:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對哦，不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.74,0:11:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.01,0:11:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那艘船上也有船員不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.04,0:11:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們很幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.98,0:11:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠為了我\N而死在EXILE的觸手下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.15,0:11:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.16,0:11:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道了吧，EXILE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.93,0:11:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，你的鑰匙就在這裡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.63,0:11:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.03,0:11:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說艾兒‧薇絲啊\N妳知道EXILE是什麼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.31,0:11:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有知道的權利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.08,0:11:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.48,0:12:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我安靜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.15,0:12:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒‧薇絲，讓我來告訴妳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.12,0:12:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE其實就是\N很久以前的移民船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,移民船？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.33,0:12:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.39,0:12:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是創造了這個世界的人們\N當初所搭乘的船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.56,0:12:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要坐上了這個\N就可以前往別的世界了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.97,0:12:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謠言這東西還真可怕呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.74,0:12:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀之戰艦不也是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.77,0:12:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼殺無赦的銀之戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.51,0:12:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼EXILE是最終兵器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.71,0:12:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎喲，真可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.28,0:12:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把人家說成殺人毀滅的道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.95,0:12:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是不是顯示出地上的人\N想要毀滅這個世界的願望啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.95,0:12:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要好好珍惜願望才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.72,0:12:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這才有夢想嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.59,0:12:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正因為有夢\N地上的人們才會辛勞工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.53,0:12:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此，讓大家繼續做夢\N就是我的義務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.67,0:12:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直漂流在大風暴區的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.70,0:12:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該還是由我來掌管不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.01,0:13:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不能隨便讓別人給看見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.76,0:13:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒‧薇絲，妳過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.92,0:13:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，不要過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.63,0:13:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.13,0:13:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在…這裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.87,0:13:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE，你看清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.07,0:14:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你從漫長的睡眠裡\N喚醒的鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.91,0:14:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.24,0:14:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可愛的艾兒‧薇絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.31,0:14:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始主角就是妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.38,0:14:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希卡達，把詩人帶來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.09,0:14:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屬下遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.02,0:14:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.37,0:14:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.08,0:14:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.01,0:14:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.58,0:14:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在要讓你看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.55,0:14:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是在這片天空所發生的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.79,0:14:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是在這片天空裡\N即將要發生的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.41,0:15:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩人先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.74,0:15:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你藏著的言靈告訴我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.41,0:15:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你再抗拒也沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.55,0:15:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的心已經被這花刺所帶的\N真實的血清給侵蝕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.90,0:15:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當初你們駕著這架先鋒艇\N來到銀之戰艦上時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.43,0:15:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長曾經這麼跟我說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.54,0:15:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說你們很像以前的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.81,0:15:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得克勞士他飛在一個\N比我們還要更高的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.25,0:15:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.18,0:15:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不能沒有他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他那人雖然頑固
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.32,0:16:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但對我和周遭的人\N其實算是滿體貼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.29,0:16:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.46,0:16:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一下子不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.80,0:16:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我…感覺一蹶不振
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.23,0:16:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不曉得該怎麼振作起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.41,0:16:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜，艾麗絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.11,0:16:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳們救救克勞士，救救艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.68,0:16:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求妳們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.08,0:16:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們答應妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.25,0:16:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會把他們救出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.95,0:16:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩人先生，來為我唸首詩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.42,0:16:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唸那首遠古時代的覺醒之詩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.89,0:16:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧，亞力克斯‧羅威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.13,0:16:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡為我說出關鍵謎詩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.14,0:16:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先是達格貝家的謎詩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.08,0:17:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把大地染成金色的波浪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.88,0:17:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撫育生命萬物之氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.65,0:17:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小麥之…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.46,0:17:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.24,0:17:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巨繭產生反應了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.54,0:17:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真傻，亞力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.88,0:17:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果打一開始你老老實實唸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.35,0:17:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不用受這種罪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.55,0:17:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己不好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.68,0:17:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.02,0:17:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉乖孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.09,0:17:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以幫我看著你的朋友別動嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.16,0:17:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不希望有太多雜音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.90,0:17:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屬下遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.17,0:17:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧，亞力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.24,0:17:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次換漢彌爾敦家的謎詩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.37,0:18:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在記憶的彼方…存在的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.28,0:18:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切誕生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.42,0:18:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切回歸的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.99,0:18:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藍色的…星球…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.81,0:18:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現身分不明的音源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.24,0:18:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是動力音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.88,0:18:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該是剛才那道光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.31,0:18:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.85,0:18:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巨繭的雷射掃描似乎是結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.32,0:18:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞力克斯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.15,0:18:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已經被戴芬妮攻陷了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.73,0:19:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，接著唸巴席安努家的謎詩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.24,0:19:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.44,0:19:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.18,0:19:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不可能不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.45,0:19:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該已經拿到所有的謎詩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.72,0:19:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.26,0:19:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.86,0:19:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不可能違抗得了\N真實的血清的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.97,0:19:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴芬妮陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.17,0:19:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個男人或許真的不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.64,0:19:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.61,0:19:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.61,0:19:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為你這樣就瞞得過我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.78,0:19:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.52,0:19:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.89,0:19:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.16,0:19:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.46,0:20:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你身邊應該有人知道\N巴席安努家的謎詩才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.00,0:20:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.78,0:20:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個乖孩子，亞力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.09,0:20:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希達卡，把皇帝帶到這裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.96,0:20:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屬下遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.34,0:20:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.61,0:20:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來今天的關鍵謎詩\N只能唸到這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.51,0:20:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次再繼續吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.48,0:20:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手，妳不要碰艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.02,0:20:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴芬妮陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.55,0:20:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宣誓儀式的典禮會場\N有連絡進來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.12,0:21:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，結束了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.86,0:21:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧，你成為大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.83,0:21:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼承總帥頭銜的是迪奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.13,0:21:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我倆一同來繼承\N艾拉克萊家的祕技吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.14,0:21:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我們回去為迪奧慶祝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.84,0:21:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉，把艾兒‧薇絲帶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.51,0:22:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.35,0:22:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那邊那位朋友也一起帶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.12,0:22:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精彩的還在後頭呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.62,0:22:39.75,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜的時光逐漸逼近\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜の時間が迫り来る
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.46,0:22:46.89,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你離我如此接近感覺  卻好遠…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたはこんな近く でも遠い…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.96,0:22:51.59,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你的憧憬是什麼\N{\c&HFFBF00&}何に憧れて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.67,0:22:57.47,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,心中想的又是誰\N{\c&HFFBF00&}だれを想うのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.54,0:23:03.10,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你奮不顧身的身影\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いのち賭ける姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.18,0:23:12.11,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,有一種透明的美麗  令我噤聲無言\N{\c&HFFBF00&}透き通る美しさに 言葉を飲んだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.19,0:23:17.92,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你欲飛往天際\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたが空を行くなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.99,0:23:24.59,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我願成為你的翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}わたしは翼になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.66,0:23:29.90,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,無論風有多麼強\N{\c&HFFBF00&}どんなに強い風にも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.97,0:23:35.43,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,也永遠不會折斷的柔婉翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}けして折れない しなやかな羽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.51,0:23:48.01,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,相信有一天  我會擁有那樣一對翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いつか　きっと持つから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.99,0:23:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（下回預告）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.99,0:23:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧身體裡那個壞孩子\N已經不在了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.60,0:23:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.53,0:23:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡聽話的迪奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.20,0:24:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我為我可愛的迪奧\N帶來了獎品送你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.10,0:24:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.51,0:24:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫他取個名字吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.11,0:24:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一回，最後流亡 第23話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.88,0:24:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騎士魯修拉\NCastling Lucciola
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.98,0:24:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.25,0:24:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起你的名字就叫魯修拉
